  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he bought like in the woods, wood, and came very-- he hired many wagons with horses, very-- you know the drivers-- and they came there and they picked up woods, which was already taking an order who ordered when they were [INAUDIBLE] to get to the wood, you know, to everybody.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started, since then, to help out my father and this business.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How did I do it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He left me names who ordered and gave them a deposit.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Whenever-- he used to be completely in the back of all the wagons, probably by a reason, OK.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he knew that he may depend on me, although I was a very young girl-- maybe I was in the age of 10.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I don't know-- more or less.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they came and to each wagon had consisted of a certain amount of-- kilos or something.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I looked up the that and that what my husband-- my father left for me that-- what shall I say?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they knew I-- to whom, you know, the orders, the orders, the home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- I've done my job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went really-- I sat down on the-- on the wagon and showed the drivers how to drive into that and that family, all around.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since then, I felt my father-- [INAUDIBLE] used to say this-- when I will grow up, I will become-- I will be a good business woman.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And how many sisters and brothers did you have?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had only one sister, her name was Pearl, and one brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name was Israel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Israel.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Well, then we were in Israel, I found out if a friend which was a friend of my mother.",
